name: Greyson_Living_Hampton_Dark_Brown_Cherry_62-inch_Round_Dining_Table
reviews: I LOVE this table. It can fit 9 chairs around it. It's very sturdy,it's exactly what I wanted. I've gotten so many compliment's. Buy it!
gorgeous finish on the table top. lots of space under to put your chairs. really beautiful. dark wood

Very nice table. Looks great in my dining room. I put different color parsons chairs around it and it really looks great. This can fit 4 to 6 chairs. I like that it's big enough without a leaf . I wanted round not oval. Looks high quality. The only assemble is putting on legs, not a big deal.
Exactly the style of table I was looking for my dining area. The color was perfect to match the bakers's rack. Good quality.
I have been looking forever for a round table that was big enough to seat more than four people and that wouldn't break the bank. This was it!! Very affordable and just beautiful table all around.
